WEBVTT

00:07:29.860 --> 00:07:32.660
it’s good to keep fighting
in your relationships,

00:07:32.870 --> 00:07:35.240
it’s good to keep nurturing
your relationships.

00:07:35.240 --> 00:07:37.010
And the biggest thing he said was

00:07:37.010 --> 00:07:39.250
that taking dowry is a sin, but…

00:07:39.250 --> 00:07:41.960
KJ: Sorry, that was a
politically incorrect statement,

00:07:41.960 --> 00:07:45.400
but I meant emotional dowry.
SRK: That’s what I was saying.

00:07:45.410 --> 00:07:48.740
Taking material gifts in dowry is wrong
for both the boy and the girl,

00:07:48.740 --> 00:07:50.400
but if you do want to take dowry,

00:07:50.400 --> 00:07:52.790
take a dowry of relationships
to each other’s homes

00:07:52.790 --> 00:07:54.920
and always nurture those relationships.

00:07:54.920 --> 00:07:57.090
Thank you so much Karan Johar

00:07:57.090 --> 00:08:00.920
and our love for Yash and Roohi.
God bless you.